## 3. Spacing & Layout

### Spacing Scale (strict adherence)
```
0.5  (2px)   → Icon padding, tight gaps
1    (4px)   → Between related items
2    (8px)   → Standard small gap
3    (12px)  → Input padding, card padding
4    (16px)  → Section padding, component gaps
6    (24px)  → Card padding, section margins
8    (32px)  → Page section gaps
12   (48px)  → Major section separation
16   (64px)  → Page top/bottom padding
```

### Layout Principles
- Max content width: `max-w-6xl` (1152px) or `max-w-7xl` (1280px)
- Page padding: `px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`
- Card padding: `p-4` or `p-6` — never `p-5` or odd values
- Consistent vertical rhythm with `space-y-*` utilities

### Grid System
```tsx
// Standard page layout
<div className="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div className="space-y-8">
    {/* content */}
  </div>
</div>
```

