## 4. Component Patterns

### Buttons
```tsx
// Primary
<Button className="bg-gray-900 text-white hover:bg-gray-800">

// Secondary
<Button variant="outline" className="border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-50">

// Ghost
<Button variant="ghost" className="hover:bg-gray-100">
```

**Button Rules:**
- Height: `h-9` (36px) standard, `h-8` (32px) compact
- Padding: `px-4` standard, `px-3` compact
- Border radius: `rounded-md` (6px) — NEVER fully rounded (`rounded-full`) for action buttons
- Text: `text-sm font-medium`

### Cards
```tsx
<div className="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6">
```

**Card Rules:**
- Border: Always use `border border-gray-200`
- Shadow: Minimal or none (`shadow-sm` max) — NEVER `shadow-lg` or `shadow-xl`
- Border radius: `rounded-lg` (8px)
- No gradient backgrounds

### Inputs
```tsx
<Input className="h-9 border-gray-200 focus:border-gray-400 focus:ring-gray-400" />
```

**Input Rules:**
- Height: `h-9` (36px) to match buttons
- Border: `border-gray-200`, focus: `border-gray-400`
- Background: `bg-white` or `bg-gray-50`
- Placeholder: `text-gray-400`

### Tables
- Header: `bg-gray-50 text-gray-500 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider`
- Rows: `border-b border-gray-100` 
- Hover: `hover:bg-gray-50`

