## 5. Animation & Interaction

### Transition Defaults
```tsx
// Standard transition
className="transition-colors duration-150"

// Interactive elements
className="transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
```

### Animation Rules
- Duration: 150-200ms for micro-interactions
- Easing: `ease-out` for enters, `ease-in` for exits
- Prefer `transform` and `opacity` (GPU-accelerated)
- No bouncing, no spring animations in UI

### Focus States
```tsx
className="focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gray-400 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
```

### Hover States
- Subtle background change: `hover:bg-gray-50` or `hover:bg-gray-100`
- Never change multiple properties on hover
- No scale transforms on buttons or cards

