## 6. Icons

### Icon Library
- Use `lucide-react` (already included with shadcn)
- Icon size: Match text — `size={16}` with `text-sm`, `size={20}` with `text-base`
- Icon color: `text-gray-400` or `text-gray-500` for decorative, inherit for actionable
- Stroke width: Keep default (2) — never modify

### Icon + Text Pairing
```tsx
<Button>
  <Icon className="mr-2 h-4 w-4" />
  Label
</Button>
```

