## 7. Forbidden Patterns (AI Slop)

### NEVER Do This:
1. **Purple/violet gradients** on white backgrounds
2. **Multiple font families** in one view
3. **Excessive shadows** (shadow-md, shadow-lg, shadow-xl on cards)
4. **Rounded-full buttons** for primary actions
5. **Emoji in UI** unless explicitly for user content
6. **Colorful icons** — stick to monochrome
7. **Hero sections with stock gradients**
8. **Glowing effects** or neon colors
9. **Multiple competing accent colors**
10. **Skeleton loaders with animation** that draws attention

### NEVER Use These Patterns:
```tsx
// ❌ BAD - Gradient button
<button className="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500">

// ❌ BAD - Excessive shadow
<div className="shadow-xl rounded-2xl">

// ❌ BAD - Pill button for actions
<button className="rounded-full px-8">

// ❌ BAD - Colorful icons
<Icon className="text-purple-500" />
```

### DO This Instead:
```tsx
// ✅ GOOD - Solid, minimal button
<button className="bg-gray-900 text-white rounded-md px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium">

// ✅ GOOD - Clean card
<div className="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg bg-white p-6">

// ✅ GOOD - Subtle icon
<Icon className="text-gray-400 h-4 w-4" />
```

