## 9. File Organization

```
/app
  /layout.tsx          # Root layout with fonts
  /page.tsx            # Homepage
  /(routes)/           # Route groups
/components
  /ui/                 # ShadCN components (do not modify heavily)
  /[feature]/          # Feature-specific components
/lib
  /utils.ts            # Utility functions (cn, etc.)
/styles
  /globals.css         # Tailwind imports + CSS variables
```

---

## 10. Quality Checklist

Before shipping any UI:

- [ ] Only gray-50 or white backgrounds used
- [ ] No shadows larger than shadow-sm
- [ ] All text uses IBM Plex Sans font family
- [ ] Headings have tight letter-spacing (-0.02em to -0.03em)
- [ ] Buttons have consistent height (h-8 or h-9)
- [ ] Cards have border-gray-200, no gradients
- [ ] Focus states are visible (ring-2)
- [ ] Spacing uses standard scale (4, 6, 8, 12, 16)
- [ ] Icons are gray-400/gray-500, not colorful
- [ ] No purple gradients anywhere
- [ ] Typography hierarchy is clear (max 3 sizes per view)
